# Environment Variables & Security

- **Validation:** All env vars must be validated in `src/env.ts` using a Zod schema. Throw a descriptive error on missing or invalid values at build/runtime.
- **Documentation:** When a new env var is added to `src/env.ts`, prompt to add a placeholder to `.env.example`.
- **Git Safety:** Any new sensitive files (`.env.local`, `.pnpm-debug.log`, etc.) must be added to `.gitignore`.
